  "title": "Aircraft Technician / Aerospace Technician",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>Well Established Company</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Basic $2500 - $2800 + Variable Bonus</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working location: North</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working day: Monday to Friday</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working hours: 8.30am to 6pm</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>TRAINING PROVIDED</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Refurbish aircraft cabin interior components</li>\n  <li>Perform visual and dimensional inspection of aircraft cabin interior components</li>\n  <li>Perform receiving inspection, disassembly, cleaning, repair and painting</li>\n  <li>Perform scheduled maintenance and housekeeping tasks</li>\n  <li>Other ad hoc duties as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess minimum Secondary Education</li>\n  <li>Relevant experience in the aerospace industry preferred</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now </strong>button with the following information in the resume</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li>\n  <li>Current and Expected salary</li>\n  <li>Reason for leaving</li>\n  <li>Date of availability</li>\n  <li>Education background</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>LIONG ZHAO GUAN (R22107632)</p>\n<p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
